{"skipTransitionList":[],"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_01","textHome":"美术品真是漂亮啊。我正在水名美术馆打工。@因为我的梦想是成为美术品修复师，@所以就打算从接近美术品开始。@虽然也有过挫折，但大家却都温柔地带着我，@所以我会一直努力！下次，记得来我这玩哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_18","textHome":"父亲他，生前也是从事美术方面的工作的。@所以，我也想从事这方面的工作。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_19","textHome":"我变强了！我变强了对吧……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":303200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_20","textHome":"我感觉力量涌了出来……我会更加努力的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_21","textHome":"我在成为魔法少女之前，从来没有拿过武器，@也没有和人吵过架。@所以，我稍微有些害怕战斗。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":303200,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_22","textHome":"不管和魔女还有使魔战斗了多少次，@我都没办法习惯……一直都是畏手畏脚的……@因为感觉很害怕。@不过，这城市……神滨……水名……@都是我最喜欢的地方。@所以我必须要守护这里。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_23","textHome":"我想过了，为什么我会这么喜欢这城市呢……@因为这城市历史悠久，虽然并没有在文献中@留存下来，但是在这里生活的人们都和我息@息相关。我喜欢这样的城市……所以我也想@伴随着这城市。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_24","textHome":"我好孤单……能见到你真是太好了，诶嘿嘿。@一直在等吗？嗯，我一直在等你！@我好想快点见到你。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_25","textHome":"早上好。@诶嘿嘿，从早上就能见到你真是太开心了……@早起的鸟儿有虫吃是真的呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_26","textHome":"说好了这次要做便当的，我该做些什么呢？@诶？不，不是带去学校的便当，@是带去我打工的地方的啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_27","textHome":"啊，到打工时间了……我要去美术馆工作了。@要是有空的话，就来看看吧。@那里有很多饱经沧桑的美术品哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_03","textHome":"要是爸爸还活着，是不是就是这样的感觉呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_28","textHome":"呼哈……嗯……@到了晚上气温也下降了，稍微有些冷呢……@这个时候要是有人陪在我旁边就好了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_29","textHome":"在展览馆空闲的时间，@我会去观摩美术品的修复工作，@不知不觉就会忘记了时间。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_30","textHome":"差不多该去消灭魔女了吧？@我虽然还不习惯战斗，@但是我会竭尽全力帮上忙的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_31","textHome":"虽然知道它们是敌人，@但同样是魔法少女的样子，好难下手……@不过必须要战斗……@我……我会加油的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_32","textHome":"我是要和这里的人一起战斗呢。@我明白了！@我会做好被分配的任务的，一起加油吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_33","textHome":"我真的很怕生……@我完全不知道应该和初次见面的人说些什么……@不过，和你聊天倒是很容易啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_34","textHome":"啊！……好痛，又摔倒了。@糟糕！资料散了一地……@嗯——之前是按什么顺序的？@诶？是什么样来着？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_35","textHome":"那个……有时间吗……想要你再陪我一会儿。@不过……你要有事情的话，@我也不会强求你就是了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_36","textHome":"想看我是怎么样介绍展品的么？@咳咳「这件是在日本十分少见的绘发……」@啊，咬到舌头了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_37","textHome":"美术馆的工作真的很有趣。@我本来就喜欢古代美术品和历史悠久的建筑，@而且这让我感觉离梦想又近了一步。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_04","textHome":"我……这不是我的本意……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_38","textHome":"它们本来是什么样子的呢……@是怎么样被爱护着的呢……@我喜欢这样的想象，@所以我想要成为美术品的修复师。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_39","textHome":"沙优希还想多听一些关于刀的故事，@但我工作太忙了……@反正在同一个学校，下次白天再邀请她吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_40","textHome":"莉爱总是对我说「强硬一点」@但是怎么样才能「强硬」呢？@「变强」！@是这样吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_41","textHome":"你总是在寂寞的时候陪着我……@我很开心……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_42","textHome":"虽然有些害怕……但我会努力的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_43","textHome":"嗯？诶？我赢了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303200}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_44","textHome":"哈啊～胜利了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_45","textHome":"我会努力的！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_46","textHome":"诶嘿嘿，好开心。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_63","textHome":"既然被拜托了，我就要做到底！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_05","textHome":"我喜欢可靠的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_64","textHome":"嗯……这边这样……然后那样……"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_65","textHome":"死心吧！到此为止了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_66","textHome":"已经了结了！对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_02","textHome":"我叫梢麻友。那个，我……虽然有点怕生，@但我并不喜欢自己一个人待着……@我喜欢和别人待在一起。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_13","textHome":"嗯……我，变强了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_14","textHome":"我感觉变强了。这样我就能更加努力了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_15","textHome":"嗯，我们去下个展区吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_16","textHome":"我的父亲，在我很小的时候就因事故去世了。@现在是我和我的母亲相依为命。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_17","textHome":"有时，我会幻想我的父亲还活着。@好想和他聊聊各种关于美术的话题啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}